---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 395
  - Title: Bhagavad-Gîtâ
    Location: XVIII 59
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Holy War=Injunction to Holy War
  - 329
---
If, actuated by egoism, thou thinkest： 'I will not fight.’ in vain is
this thy resolve. Thine own nature will impel thee.
